<h3 id="deployment-only">Deployment-only</h3>

<p>Each platform that supports running Swift applications is required to provide documentation for getting started. The documentation should contain information for installing Swift, using the REPL, using the Swift Package Manager and using the Debugger. Every platform is expected to have core runtime, Standard Library support, and core libraries, except where explicitly documented otherwise.</p>

